576
00:26:13.196 --> 00:26:16.074
-Buongiorno. Signora Alessia.
-Ah. buongiorno. Giuseppe.

577
00:26:19.286 --> 00:26:22.122
(gasps) Oh. God. Oh. no.

578
00:26:25.250 --> 00:26:26.751
-(screaming)
-(gasps)

579
00:26:28.461 --> 00:26:29.838
-(gasps)
-(screams)

580
00:26:29.879 --> 00:26:31.089
NONNA ALESSIA:
Oh Dio!

581
00:26:32.716 --> 00:26:34.926
(sighs)

582
